    println("")
    println("cost estimate (Mac local): $0 — bio axes run as C0b skeletons by default;")
    println("                            weave empirical paths via HEXA_BIO_WITH_NUMPY=1;")
    println("                            `quantum` status snapshot is pure hexa (full VQE = local Aer + ANU QRNG).")
    println("")
